0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37118,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/12\/dua-leaving-lavatory\/","url_meta":{"origin":34661,"position":1},"title":"Abu Dharr on Bathrooms: Supplication for exiting the toilet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 12, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ali al-Sayqal reported: Abu Dharr, may Allah be pleased with him, when he left the washroom, he would say, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah, who has removed harm from me and granted me wellness.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 10 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15272,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/dua-prophet-finishing-meal\/","url_meta":{"origin":34661,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet\u2019s supplication for finishing meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say when he cleared the table of his meal, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah, abundantly, purely, and blessed in it, yet such praise is neither enough, nor abandoned, nor is it without need, Our Lord.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32848,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/21\/praise-allah-who-fed-me\/","url_meta":{"origin":34661,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Eating: Praise be to Allah who fed me","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever eats a meal and says, \u2018All praise is due to Allah, who fed me this from his provision without any capability or strength on my part,\u2019 his previous minor sins will be forgiven.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15269,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/dua-eating-bismillah-suffice\/","url_meta":{"origin":34661,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Eating: Remembering Allah is enough","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was eating with six of his companions when a bedouin came and ate all of the food in two bites. The Prophet said, \u201cIf he had mentioned the name of Allah, it would have been enough for all of you.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26776,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/27\/dua-barakah-food-drink\/","url_meta":{"origin":34